<paragraph blockId="47.[151,1437,999,1457]" pageId="47" pageNumber="48">
Remarks.— 
<bibRefCitation author="Distant, W. L." box="[285,450,999,1025]" pageId="47" pageNumber="48" pagination="335 - 338" refId="ref67810" refString="Distant, W. L. (1882) Descriptions of a new species and a new genus of Cicadidae from Madagascar. Transaction of the Royal Entomological Society of London, 1882, 335 - 338, plate XV. https: // doi. org / 10.1111 / j. 1365 - 2311.1882. tb 01579. x" type="journal article" year="1882">Distant (1882)</bibRefCitation>
included the eyes much narrower than the base of the pronotum (variable now across species of the genus but still narrower than pronotum), ocelli distant from the posterior head, moderately long antennae with a thickened scape, anteriorly narrowed pronotum, amplified pronotal collar lateral angle, rostrum reaching the posterior coxae, hyaline wings with divergence of the distal subcostal and radius anterior 1 veins, eight fore wing apical cells with apical cell 1 longer than apical cell 2, bases of veins separating ulnar cells parallel, basal cell considerably longer than broad, hind wings with six apical cell, globose male abdomen, strongly convex dorsally and flattened ventrally, attenuated apical segment, separate membranes on the first and second abdominal sternites, opercula not covering tympanal cavity, and strongly spined anterior femora as characteristic of the genus.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="47.[151,1437,999,1457]" pageId="47" pageNumber="48">
For many years 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Distant" authorityYear="1882" box="[387,507,1287,1313]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadidae" genus="Malagasia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="47" pageNumber="48" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[387,507,1287,1313]" italics="true" pageId="47" pageNumber="48">Malagasia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
represented a genus where species from 
<collectingCountry box="[980,1115,1287,1313]" name="Madagascar" pageId="47" pageNumber="48">Madagascar</collectingCountry>
without timbal covers were classified. Half of these species were transferred to 
<taxonomicName authority="Boulard, 2008" authorityName="Boulard" authorityYear="2008" box="[722,1031,1323,1349]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadidae" genus="Anopercalna" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="47" pageNumber="48" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[722,866,1323,1349]" italics="true" pageId="47" pageNumber="48">Anopercalna</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Boulard, M." box="[872,1031,1323,1349]" pageId="47" pageNumber="48" pagination="161 - 178" refId="ref67371" refString="Boulard, M. (2008) Statuts et ethologies sonores de quatre cigales malgaches, trois sont nouvelles et deux representent un nouveau genre et une nouvelle sous-tribu (Rhynchota, Auchenorhyncha Cicadidae). Lambillionea, CVIII, 161 - 178." type="book chapter" year="2008">Boulard, 2008</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
since they were originally classified in 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Distant" authorityYear="1882" box="[180,300,1359,1385]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadidae" genus="Malagasia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="47" pageNumber="48" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[180,300,1359,1385]" italics="true" pageId="47" pageNumber="48">Malagasia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="47.[151,1437,999,1457]" pageId="47" pageNumber="48">
Distribution.—Species of the genus are restricted to 
<collectingCountry box="[780,915,1395,1421]" name="Madagascar" pageId="47" pageNumber="48">Madagascar</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Metcalf, Z. P." box="[928,1095,1395,1421]" pageId="47" pageNumber="48" pagination="1 - 585" refId="ref69829" refString="Metcalf, Z. P. (1963 a) General catalogue of the Homoptera, Fascicle VIII. Cicadoidea. Part 1. Cicadidae. Section I. Tibiceninae. North Carolina State College Contribution, 1502, i-vii + 1 - 585." type="journal article" year="1963">Metcalf 1963a</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Duffels, J. P. &amp; van der Laan, P. A." box="[1105,1431,1394,1421]" pageId="47" pageNumber="48" refId="ref68709" refString="Duffels, J. P. &amp; van der Laan, P. A. (1985) Catalogue of the Cicadoidea (Homoptera, Auchenorhyncha) 1956 - 1980. Series Entomologica 34. Dr. W. Junk Publishers, Dordrect, 414 pp." type="book" year="1985">Duffels &amp; van der Laan 1985</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Sanborn, A. F." box="[151,313,1431,1457]" pageId="47" pageNumber="48" refId="ref70566" refString="Sanborn, A. F. (2013) Catalogue of the Cicadoidea (Hemiptera: Cicadoidea). With contributions to the bibliography by Martin H. Villet. Elsevier / Academic Press, San Diego, 1001 pp. https: // doi. org / 10.1016 / b 978 - 0 - 12 - 416647 - 9.00001 - 2" type="book" year="2013">Sanborn 2013</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
